  Modern Gaming-Themed 404 Page for BloxMania
  Features:
  - Gaming-inspired design with animated elements
  - Interactive background effects
  - Modern glassmorphism styling
  - Font Awesome icons throughout
  - Responsive design with mobile optimizations
  - Engaging animations and hover effects
{% endcomment %}

<div class="error-404-section">
  <!-- Animated Background -->
  <div class="error-404__background" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="error-404__particles">
      <div class="star star--1">★</div>
      <div class="star star--2">★</div>
      <div class="star star--3">★</div>
      <div class="star star--4">★</div>
      <div class="star star--5">★</div>
      <div class="star star--6">★</div>
      <div class="star star--7">★</div>
      <div class="star star--8">★</div>
      <div class="star star--9">★</div>
      <div class="star star--10">★</div>
      <div class="star star--11">★</div>
      <div class="star star--12">★</div>
    </div>
